### Image Upload API Documentation

# Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### 1. Upload Product Image
POST {{baseUrl}}/upload/image
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

# Note: This is a multipart/form-data request
# Use a tool like Postman or curl to test this endpoint
# Form field name: "image"
# File: select an image file

### 2. Get All Uploaded Images
GET {{baseUrl}}/upload/images
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Delete Image
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/upload/image/product-1234567890-123456789.jpg
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Upload Image with cURL (Example)
# curl -X POST \
#   -H "Authorization: Bearer {{token}}" \
#   -F "image=@/path/to/your/image.jpg" \
#   {{baseUrl}}/upload/image

### 5. Upload Image with JavaScript (Example)
